nodes.title: Prompt Guide
widgets_values:
_This is essentially Crody's guide boiled down._

# Prompt format

- 1: Quality tags, styles and ratings
- 2: Person count and interaction
- 3: Character identifier, then describe them from head to toe
- 4: Posing excluding interaction
- (Repeat 3 & 4 for each character, optionally with break between)
- 6: Camera position and background
- BREAK
- 7: Lighting, Depth and After details

nodes.title: Negative Prompt Text
widgets_values: overexposure, bright light, bad quality video, worst quality, deformed face, bad teeth, poor eyes, deformed eyes, aliasing,pixelation, character is not moving, arms standing still, motion blur, blurry, noise, censored, talking, blurred characters, noisy characters, bad quality hands, stiff characters, bad eyes, ugly eyes, stiff motion, motion artifacts, blurry motion, quick mouth motion, fast talking, blurry face, blurry eyes, artifacted eyes, static, bullet time, slow motion, bullet time effect
Bypass the WanVideoNAG to disable negative prompting. Sometimes negative prompting can end up causing the undesired behaviour - I'm not sure why.
Bypass FLF node and route I2V if you don't want looping videos.
The final detailed image is routed over here.
Optionally clean memory when done generation.
The Save Video node likes to expand on playback anyways, so I'm not even going to pretend like it'll fit in a group nicely.

nodes.title: Positive Prompt Text
widgets_values:
Very high quality 4k drawn animation, 4k resolution, smooth motion, realistic movement, natural movement, fast motion,

a girl rides atop of a large wolf. The wolf is standing and looks at the camera. Snow falls from the sky slowly. Trees sway with the wind. The girls hair blows in the wind.
NSFW LoRA's give pretty good prompt adherence.

nodes.title: Positive Prompt Text
widgets_values:
H4perrealistic, extremely detailed, masterpiece, photorealistic, sfw, enchanting eyes, focus on eyes and face and hair,

1girl, 1wolf
A young girl riding on a large wolf in the winter,

girl, detailed hair, brown hair, white hoodie,

BREAK,

wolf, large wolf, standing, a girl is riding the wolf, fluffy, yellow eyes,

side view, viewed from the side, outside, forest path, pine trees,
snow, snowing, winter, pine trees, wind, close up, full body, centered image, looking at viewer,

I slam everything through an image filter so I can select which image to pass to the video generator. Sometimes eyes/hands/face/genitals get worse in the detailer, but usually only when the prompts aren't up to date.

Often it's OK to pipe the full prompt in, but sometimes it'll take the mask area and render a full character where there should be a hand or genital.

Images are in order of [original] -> [eyes] -> [eyes + hands] -> [final]
